I"i<p>The BUDS Lab hosts the first <a href="https://www.edx.org/course/Data-Science-for-Construction-Architecture-and-Engineering">online data science course</a> focused <strong>specifically on data analytics from the various phases of the building life cycle - design, construction, and operations.</strong> This is an introductory course that adds <a href="https://www.python.org/">Python</a>, the <a href="https://pandas.pydata.org/">Pandas Data Analytics library</a> and various visualization and machine learning techniques to the toolbox of architects, engineers, operations, and other industry professionals.</p>
